name: test signing key key is added and imported

steps.name: Given SecurityServer login page is open
And Page is prepared to be tested
And User xrd logs in to SecurityServer with password secret
Given healthcheck has errors and error message is "No certificate chain available in authentication key."
And Keys and certificates tab is selected
And Token: softToken-0 is present and expanded
When Token: softToken-0 - Add key wizard is opened
And Key Label is set to "test signing key"
And CSR details Usage is set to "SIGNING", Client set to "DEV:COM:1234", Certification Service to "Test CA" and CSR format "PEM"
And Generate "SIGNING" CSR is set to DNS "ss0" and Organization "ui-test"
And CSR with extension "pem" successfully generated
And Token: softToken-0 - has key with label "test signing key"
Then CSR is processed by test CA
And Token: softToken-0 - Generated certificate is imported
And Token: softToken-0 - has key "test signing key" with status "Registered"
And Token: softToken-0 - has "SIGNING" key "test signing key" with correct fixed automatic renewal status

$("By.xpath: //tbody[ tr/td/div[@class ='name-wrap-top']//div[contains(@class,'identifier-wrap')]//span[text() = 'test signing key']]//div[@data-test='renewal-status']") should be(text "NEXT PLANNED RENEWAL ON 2044-10-19")

$("By.xpath: //tbody[ tr/td/div[@class ='name-wrap-top']//div[contains(@class,'identifier-wrap')]//span[text() = 'test signing key']]//div[@data-test='renewal-status']") should be(text "NEXT PLANNED RENEWAL ON 2044-10-19")
And Token: softToken-0, key "test signing key" generate CSR button is disabled

$("By.xpath: //div[@class='exp-wrapper expandable']//div[span[text()='Token: softToken-0']]//following::tr[@data-test='key-row' and td//span[text() = 'test signing key']]//button[@data-test='generate-csr-button']") should be(disabled)

$("By.xpath: //div[@class='exp-wrapper expandable']//div[span[text()='Token: softToken-0']]//following::tr[@data-test='key-row' and td//span[text() = 'test signing key']]//button[@data-test='generate-csr-button']") should be(disabled)
